Stacked bar plot of the number alpha/beta chains paired by each pairing algorithm

plot_paired.Rd

Stacked bar plot of the number alpha/beta chains paired by each pairing algorithm

Usage

plot_paired(
  data,
  chain = c("paired", "alpha", "beta"),
  samples = NULL,
  color_scheme = NULL
)

Arguments

data

a TIRTLseqData object or a data frame created using get_pair_stats()

chain

the TCR chain to plot (default is "paired")

samples

(optional) the samples to include in the plot (default is all)

color_scheme

(optional) the color scheme for the plot

See also

Other plotting: plot_clone_size_across_samples(), plot_clonotype_indices(), plot_clusters(), plot_diversity(), plot_n_reads(), plot_num_partners(), plot_paired_by_read_fraction_range(), plot_paired_vs_rank(), plot_pairs_with_eachother(), plot_ranks(), plot_read_fraction_vs_pair_status(), plot_sample_overlap(), plot_sample_vs_sample()
